thread.title_full: Precision Tax Relief reviewed by Randria Robinson

author: Randria Robinson
title: Randria Robinson
text: I went in stressed out the IRS had placed a levy on my paycheck thy immediately stepped in stopped the levy and started to work things out no we are at the end and they have changed my life I can sleep not afraid to go to the mailbox I owed 34k in back taxes and they settled with me for a little over 1,000.00 such a blessing and very thankful for all of their help!
